<L>__{exterior boat deck and a deck, aft}
<A>__{panic is setting in around the remaining boats aft. the crowd here is now a mix of all three classes. officers repeatedly warn men back from the boats. the crowd presses in closer. seamen scarott brandishes the tiller of boat 14 to discourage a close press of men who look ready to rush the boat. several men break ranks and rush forward. lightoller pulls out his webley revolver and aims it at them.}
<C>__{lightoller}
<A>__{get back! keep order! the men back down. fifth officer lowe standing in the boat, yells to the crew.}
<C>__{lowe}
<A>__{lower away left and right! lightoller turns away from the crowd and, out of their sight, breaks his pistol open. letting out a long breath, he starts to load it.}
